{"tid":904133,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貝索斯:亞馬遜終會沒落 盡力推遲這刻來臨","createTime":"2018-11-16T05:45:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-16T07:40:54.000Z","uid":28765,"like":30,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7baeaf8a2202f30f4b9bd5e976d4b71a853f2541","tid":904133,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"亞馬遜創辦人貝索斯(Jeff Bezos)認為，亞馬遜總有一天會倒閉，而員工們要做的是盡可能推遲這一刻的來臨。<br />\n<br />\n貝索斯早前在西雅圖全體員工會議上，被問及亞馬遜的未來。他回應指出，大多數的大型企業壽命一般是30多年，而不是100年以上，而亞馬遜並非大到不能倒閉。事實上，他預測有一天亞馬遜會沒落、會破產。<br />\n<br />\n貝索斯稱，推遲公司「死亡」的時間，關鍵是要關注並滿足客戶需要。如果企業開始關注自身，而並非其客戶的話，那將是企業步向完結的開端，而亞馬遜必須盡量推遲這一天的來臨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1993999/貝索斯%3A亞馬遜終會沒落+盡力推遲這刻來臨\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F1993999%2F%E8%B2%9D%E7%B4%A2%E6%96%AF%253A%E4%BA%9E%E9%A6%AC%E9%81%9C%E7%B5%82%E6%9C%83%E6%B2%92%E8%90%BD%2B%E7%9B%A1%E5%8A%9B%E6%8E%A8%E9%81%B2%E9%80%99%E5%88%BB%E4%BE%86%E8%87%A8&d=38jqZUFrbngVAerxXx0BOwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=6b94de1e\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/1993999/貝索斯%3A亞馬遜終會沒落+盡力推遲這刻來臨</a><br />\n<br />\n如日方中講d咁既野 使唔使<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b62a5c1dbd047cd7ef9a71f6b4484f9fd13ffb2","tid":904133,"uid":22481,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:47:25.000Z","msg":"真係死先黎意識到就遲啦"},{"pid":"d9dae04d3f7f88cdfd9b5e09a6e6116ab946a43b","tid":904133,"uid":17616,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T05:48:57.000Z","msg":"人地呢啲叫居安思危，不斷進步"},{"pid":"6156d9d1ee441dced5dd40ac0186e23c0e1f2375","tid":904133,"uid":3704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T06:20:15.000Z","msg":"呢d先係正確態度囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb25dfe6ff15e26c5bc35cf2b3a0efa8b9b08bef","tid":904133,"uid":117200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201